                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18010701-20-defend212 t18010701-20-punish118"></join>
               Transported for seven years
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Second Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Justice Lawrence.</p>
